msgid "Sign up for GBIF’s https://www.gbif.org/newsletters[newsletter and to mailing lists^], follow GBIF on https://twitter.com/gbifnews[Twitter^] or https://www.facebook.com/gbifnews[Facebook^], and keep up to date with https://www.gbif.org/resource/search?contentType=news[news^] on the website."
